Must be willing to relocate to within commuting distance of Galloway, NJ.</li>
<li>
2+ years Linux System Administration experience.</li>
<li>
Familiarity with common Linux server applications such as Apache2, Nginx, Postfix, MySQL, BIND, etc.</li>
<li>
Ability to identify and troubleshoot TCP/IP issues, other networking issues (packet loss, connections timing out / refused).</li>
<li>
Ability to troubleshoot firewall issues, identifying problematic / misconfigured iptables rules.</li>
<li>
